  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the role of

        1. dietary calcium in fecal fat loss and the association between lactose maldigestion,
           dietary calcium level and source, and weight loss induced by caloric restriction.

        2. caloric restriction on biomarkers of inflammation and oxidative stress
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
